 "y0": 133.0, "x1": 328.0, "y1": 148.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.8857, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 0}, {"text": "本书是一本全面介绍燃气轮机及其联合循环装置的著作，书中既有理论讲解又", "box": [[139.0, 159.0], [457.0, 157.0], [458.0, 171.0], [139.0, 173.0]], "x0": 139.0, "y0": 157.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 173.0, "center_x": 298.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9946, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 1}, {"text": "对现场操作具有很强的指导性，编写本书的主要目的是为了培养燃气轮机及其联合", "box": [[121.0, 173.0], [457.0, 171.0], [458.0, 185.0], [121.0, 187.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 171.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 187.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9887, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 2}, {"text": "循环机组的运行和管理人员，并为设计研究人员提供深人学习设计、研究知识前的", "box": [[121.0, 187.0], [458.0, 185.0], [458.0, 199.0], [121.0, 201.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 185.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 201.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9943, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 3}, {"text": "理论基础。全书共分二十五章，前十三章侧重于介绍燃气轮机的工作原理、性能、", "box": [[121.0, 201.0], [457.0, 199.0], [457.0, 212.0], [121.0, 215.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 199.0, "x1": 457.0, "y1": 215.0, "center_x": 289.0, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9948, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 4}, {"text": "结构、调节控制系统以及某些必要的辅助设备和系统，后十二章则侧重于有关联合", "box": [[121.0, 215.0], [458.0, 213.0], [458.0, 227.0], [121.0, 229.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 213.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 229.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9944, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 5}, {"text": "循环方面的工作原理、余热锅炉、汽轮机、轴系布置、技术经济分析等的论述。为", "box": [[121.0, 229.0], [458.0, 227.0], [458.0, 241.0], [121.0, 242.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 227.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 242.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9829, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 6}, {"text": "了增强实用性，本书特别加强了对燃气轮机辅助设备和系统、燃气轮机和联合循环", "box": [[121.0, 243.0], [458.0, 241.0], [458.0, 255.0], [121.0, 257.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 241.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 257.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9921, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 7}, {"text": "的调节控制系统、大型燃气轮机结构、联合循环电厂的应用实例、燃气轮机和联合", "box": [[120.0, 257.0], [459.0, 254.0], [459.0, 269.0], [120.0, 272.0]], "x0": 120.0, "y0": 254.0, "x1": 459.0, "y1": 272.0, "center_x": 289.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9972, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 8}, {"text": "循环机组的运行维护及联合循环机组的性能验收试验等内容的论述。", "box": [[121.0, 271.0], [397.0, 269.0], [397.0, 283.0], [121.0, 285.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 269.0, "x1": 397.0, "y1": 285.0, "center_x": 259.0, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9926, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 9}, {"text": "本书可供从事能源、发电工程、燃气轮机及燃气一蒸汽联合循环发电装置的科", "box": [[140.0, 285.0], [458.0, 283.0], [458.0, 297.0], [140.0, 298.0]], "x0": 140.0, "y0": 283.0, "x1": 458.0, "y1": 298.0, "center_x": 299.0, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9772, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 10}, {"text": "研、管理、运行、生产的工程技术人员和大专院校的师生阅读参考。", "box": [[121.0, 300.0], [398.0, 297.0], [398.0, 310.0], [121.0, 313.0]], "x0": 121.0, "y0": 297.0, "x1": 398.0, "y1": 313.0, "center_x": 259.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9917, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 11}, {"text": "图书在版编目（CIP）数据", "box": [[152.0, 369.0], [296.0, 369.0], [296.0, 383.0], [152.0, 383.0]], "x0": 152.0, "y0": 369.0, "x1": 296.0, "y1": 383.0, "center_x": 224.0, "original_zone": "left", "confidence": 0.9913, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 12}, {"text": "燃气轮机与燃气一蒸汽联合循环装置/清华大学热能", "box": [[152.0, 393.0], [441.0, 391.0], [441.0, 407.0], [152.0, 409.0]], "x0": 152.0, "y0": 391.0, "x1": 441.0, "y1": 409.0, "center_x": 296.5, "original_zone": "wide", "confidence": 0.9966, "layout_column": "single", "reading_order_index": 13}, {"text": "工程系动力机械与工程研究所，深圳南山热电股份有限", "box": [[140.0, 411.0], [441.